<paragraph id="BA8862E56C739B30490E9B7BE820D878" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis id="4A398532DA74A9D35C4B2312922C4D4D" bold="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">Peru:</emphasis>
Pasco: Prov. Oxapampa, Oxapampa-Villa Rica road, 7 km from road head, 2120 m, 10°36'S, 75°20'W, 4 January 1984, D.N. Smith &amp; J. 
<normalizedToken id="714BE677C38E1629CA375768010C0A7E" originalValue="Albán">Alban</normalizedToken>
